  "text": "and σ W is the standard deviation of the received signal strength in a given cell. In addition, the standard deviation in the indoor office environment is set to 10 dBm [CITATION_1] . Substituting the standard deviation and the path loss exponent into Equations (5)- (7) yields the FM for 90% SR.",
